Package: git-advanced-multisync
Architecture: all
Depends: perl (>= 5.26), libmojolicious-perl, libdbi-perl, libdbd-pg-perl, postgresql, git
Description: Multi-provider Git repository sync engine with web UI
 git-advanced-multisync (gitmsyncd) synchronizes Git repositories across
 GitHub, GitLab, and Gitea through a web interface. Supports one-way and
 bidirectional sync, auto-discovery, scheduled sync, SSH and HTTPS
 transport, conflict detection, and per-profile repo management.
